  "description": "One thing recently is that I\u0026rsquo;ve kind of been acclimating to a more \u0026ldquo;normal\u0026rdquo; life, though it certainly isn\u0026rsquo;t /normal/, and normal itself is a bit of a funky concept. But in a specific context, what I mean is, I don\u0026rsquo;t have a lot of habits or routines that I see people in similar material positions have, and one way that seems true is with how I use my smartphone.\n",
